GovCloud Root Org
│
├── Platform-Security (Audit Log Viewer, Access Mgmt Admin - minimal)
│
├── ProjectA (Business Group)
│   ├── Dev Environment
│   │    ├── ProjectA-Dev-Admins      [Deploy + Full Dev control]
│   │    ├── ProjectA-Dev-Developers  [Build + Deploy + Logs]
│   │    └── ProjectA-Dev-Viewers     [Read-only]
│   │
│   ├── Test Environment
│   │    ├── ProjectA-Test-Admins     [Deploy + Test control]
│   │    └── ProjectA-Test-Testers    [Logs + Metrics only]
│   │
│   └── Production Environment
│        └── ProjectA-Prod-LogReview  [Logs + Metrics only, no deploy]
│
└── ProjectB (Business Group)
    ├── Dev Environment
    │    ├── ProjectB-Dev-Admins
    │    ├── ProjectB-Dev-Developers
    │    └── ProjectB-Dev-Viewers
    │
    ├── Test Environment
    │    ├── ProjectB-Test-Admins
    │    └── ProjectB-Test-Testers
    │
    └── Production Environment
         └── ProjectB-Prod-LogReview

